snippet.title: Rappelz Epic VIII Part 3 : Omen - Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the new Rappelz Epic VIII Part 3 - Omen trailer!

Now the time has come to take the next big step: Boss taming!

You always wondered what it would feel like to be the master of one of those deadly creatures and with the new expansion Epic 8.3 it's time to find out!

http://en.rappelz.gpotato.com/
